Description: MP3 Cover Art Manager
 A graphical application to search and add album art to MP3 files.
 Uses iTunes and Deezer APIs to automatically find covers for your songs.
 .
 Features:
  - Drag and drop MP3 files
  - Automatic cover art search from iTunes and Deezer
  - Preview and select covers before saving
  - Batch processing of multiple files
  - Support for existing cover art detection
